Package jade.tools.logging.ontology

Class LogManagementOntology

java.lang.Object
jade.content.onto.Ontology
jade.tools.logging.ontology.LogManagementOntology
All Implemented Interfaces:
LogManagementVocabulary, Serializable
public class LogManagementOntology extends Ontology implements LogManagementVocabulary
This class represents the Log-Agent-Management-ontology i.e. the set of concepts, actions and predicates needed by the LogManagerAgent and the LogHelperAgent to manage logs on JADE containers at runtime.
Author:
Giovanni Caire - TILAB
